django-openid-auth (0.5-1humbug1) wheezy; urgency=low

  * Rebase on top of current Debian unstable package. Remaining changes:
    - Modify views.py to pass along the openid_response to render_failure.
      This allows us to handle "Unknown user" responses by creating a
      PreregistrationUser.
    - Patch to support Django 1.5 in the Humbug context.

 -- Luke Faraone <lfaraone@zulip.com>  Thu, 01 Aug 2013 13:23:28 -0400

